&lt;p&gt;Kaléo is accelerating the practical use of Artificial Intelligence across the enterprise — and we’re hiring an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;AI Transformation Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to help turn AI ideas into real, usable solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands‑on, execution‑focused role for someone who already uses AI tools daily and wants to apply them to real business problems. You do not need prior “AI transformation” experience, coding skills, or pharma background. You do need curiosity, strong problem-solving instincts, and a bias toward action. The opportunity will provide you with meaningful ownership and visibility early in your career, early exposure to interacting with senior leadership for enterprise-level strategy and provide an opportunity to shape how AI is used across an organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the AI Transformation Specialist, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bring AI Into Everyday Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with teams (Finance, HR, Operations, Commercial, Legal, etc.) to identify practical opportunities for AI to save time and reduce friction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use existing AI tools (e.g., Copilot, ChatGPT Enterprise, approved internal tools) to draft and refine content, summarize and synthesize information, analyze data and trends, and build simple prototypes/demos to show what&#39;s possible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Turn Ideas Into Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help move AI use cases from “interesting idea” to real pilots and daily usage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test, iterate, and refine solutions based on user feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track progress and follow through — this role is about &lt;strong&gt;execution, not just ideation&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner Across the Organization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the AI Transformation team and functional leaders to support priority initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business needs into clear, practical AI use cases using plain language.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with stakeholders to keep initiatives moving while operating within approved guardrails.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Learn Fast and Share What Works&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn Kaléo’s business quickly and understand where time and effort are being wasted.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay curious about new AI capabilities and think creatively about internal applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share wins, lessons learned, templates, and best practices to support broader adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To be considered for the position, you must have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;0-3 years of professional experience or a recent college graduate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong, hands‑on experience using AI tools (e.g., Copilot, ChatGPT, or similar AI assistants) in real workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort experimenting with AI and figuring things out independently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to business operations, analytics, process improvement, or digital tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a structured or regulated environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bias toward action — you enjoy building, testing, and iterating.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communicator who can work with people across functions and levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized, reliable, and able to follow through on commitments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a remote opportunity with occasional travel, estimated at less than 25%.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kaléo is a global leader in drug‑delivery device technology and auto‑injector innovation, providing millions of patients, government partners, and emergency responders with security and peace of mind.&lt;/p&gt;
